{{engname|《心中有鬼》|''The Matrimony''}}是一部2007年中国惊悚爱情片，以愛情為故事主線，由[[滕华弢|滕华弢]]执导，[[黎明|黎明]]、[[刘若英|刘若英]]和[[范冰冰|范冰冰]]主演<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ent.sina.com.cn/m/c/2006-03-30/16391033063.html|title=  范冰冰與黎明攜手《心中有鬼》 港台人氣飆升|website=新浪影音娛樂|date=2006-03-30|access-date =2019-12-14|archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20060415160302/http://ent.sina.com.cn/m/c/2006-03-30/16391033063.html|archive-date =2006-04-15|dead-url =no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|language =中文|author =比華利|url =https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20060322/5756766|title =黎明愛人打孖上|publisher =蘋果日報|date =2006-03-22|access-date =2020-04-30|archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20200430042304/https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20060322/5756766|archive-date =2020-04-30|dead-url =yes}}</ref>。故事背景为30年代上海，講述黎明飾演的沈君初為愛癡狂，周旋於三三和徐曼麗之間，因難以作出抉擇而感到痛苦<ref>{{cite news |language = 中文 |url = http://paper.wenweipo.com/2007/01/26/EN0701260028.htm|title = 黎明為愛癡狂|publisher = 香港文匯報 |date = 2007-01-26 |accessdate = 2020-05-01|archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20090802213644/http://paper.wenweipo.com/2007/01/26/EN0701260028.htm|archive-date =2009-08-02|dead-url =no}}</ref>。 同名小说的作者为「一枚糖果」。

